      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WEBLEC SHIRALEE (4) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when fifth (23.32) at this track over 400m in a Grade 6. Better than latest and worth another try. ALGORITHM (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 643m behind Our Beaver (38.06) in a Grade 5/6. Was in the money the start prior. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from four starts. A big run wouldn't surprise. FEDERAL LADY (2) has shown decent speed at her last couple and filled minor placings, last time finishing second beaten 6 lengths (31.08). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Leading chance. ZIPPING THERON (6) cannot be ruled out.",
